meta.name: Naturalice Garden
meta.about:
Naturalice Garden is founded by Alice, the name "Naturalice" is created  by combining the two words, "Natural" and "Alice".  Alice has been learning the different uses of essential oils since over a decade ago. She started researching in aromatherapy, organic skin care, and holistic remedies and treatments from world-renowned organizations, and she found a lot of useful information that drove her to start a blog to share with everyone.  Our primary concern is your overall health and lifestyle.
